assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登仲有好多大愛捐血撚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死哂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161209/19859948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161209%2F19859948&d=SLpKtnFz8bAHIqZcHhNgMC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fd995fab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161209%2F19859948&h=edb5a621\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161209/19859948</a><br />\n睇下你老細加幾多人工啦<br />\n唔係冇加<br />\n只怕你冇本事加咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪出去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年個加幅 照workload計都唔撚止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥上瘦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預計到將來個制度唔變唔加人大家一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出去做好撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739f5aa7bbce20caee6aa9364f2419142b18075d","tid":267931,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"撐政府，排急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8825b5298c936f48fdb9772b0cf7259d62af00","tid":267931,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"成行因為政府唔加人同位 私人市場需求愈黎愈大<br />\n新仔慘d政府無位私家可以壓價<br />\n有經驗同肯做野跟本唔驚<br />\n私家黎緊十年都應該係再expand<br />\n因為政府已經有擴充計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係廣華瑪麗重建 同埋啓德<br />\n但加嘅位呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依幾年政府一定唔會再做野 過幾年先plan加位<br />\n到落實起碼要十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2747a01492a109305bfa4e171e7e50f0ab16010d","tid":267931,"uid":183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:51:35.000Z","msg":"新移民區<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d969ca3e8eb43adf4ac202ae18d859604522a746","tid":267931,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"快點捐血救救支那兒童"},{"pid":"fb215b0ae154418378522b86188f8098cdc037db","tid":267931,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"屯門起醫院就冇喇<br />\n起焚化爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33177d3bb08e6efde2cbb2b2b840fcf6209e9c06","tid":267931,"uid":55399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"政府減HA budget,而家無錢無人無資源<br />\n不過大家重有條港豬大橋用下"},{"pid":"018a7ea36e5e8ed64f16389c0c942cd4b5013817","tid":267931,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T17:08:05.000Z","msg":"好快又會缺血<br />\n